  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add diced onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in minced garlic and sauté for 30 seconds until fragrant.",
    "Add panang curry paste and smoked paprika, cooking for 1 minute to release aromas.",
    "Pour in vegetable broth and coconut milk, whisking to combine.",
    "Bring to a gentle simmer, add sliced carrots, and simmer for 5 minutes.",
    "Gently fold in cubed tofu and chopped kale, simmering for another 7 minutes until kale softens.",
    "Season with sea salt and lime juice, stirring to taste.",
    "Remove from heat and allow the stew to rest for 5 minutes before serving."
  ],
